Package: costcurvespkg
Type: Package
Title: Display and analyze Cost Curves and treshold choice
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2016-04-25
Author: Paulina Morillo
Maintainer: Paulina Morillo <paumoal@inf.upv.es>
Description: Tools for visualising and comparing cost curves of binary classifiers using different
    threshold choice methods.  Additionally, the library also includes functions to plot ROC curves and compute TPR (True positives rate), 
    FPR (FP False positives rate) and AUC (area under the ROC curve).
License: GPL-3
LazyData: TRUE
Imports: flux
